re to facilitate its safe and responsible management.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p>\\u00a0<\\/p><p style=\\\"line-height:1.38;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\\\" dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:hsl(0,0%,100%);color:#000000;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13.999999999999998pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\\\">In a world where privacy concerns are increasingly prevalent, XSender stands as a beacon of trust and reliability. Our dedication to data protection, stringent security measures, and commitment to safeguarding your information provide you with the peace of mind you deserve when using our services. Your privacy is our priority, and your trust in XSender is the cornerstone of our success.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p>\\u00a0<\\/p><p>\\u00a0<\\/p>\"}', 1, '2023-05-27 13:15:41', '2023-10-31 09:41:41'),
(27, NULL, 'policy_pages.element_content', '{\"title\":\"Terms and Conditions\",\"details\":\"<p><\\/p><p style=\\\"line-height:1.38;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\\\" dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13.999999999999998pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\\\"><strong>Terms and Conditions: Your Commitment to Responsible Usage<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p>\\u00a0<\\/p><p style=\\\"line-height:1.38;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\\\" dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13.999999999999998pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\\\">At [Company Name], we are dedicated to delivering high-quality email and SMS services through our bulk pricing plans. When you subscribe to these plans, you agree to the following terms and conditions to ensure a fair, secure, and reliable user experience.<\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p>\\u00a0<\\/p><p style=\\\"line-height:1.38;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\\\" dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13.999999999999998pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\\\"><strong>Service Usage: Business Purposes Only<\\/strong><\\/span><\\/span><\\/p><p>\\u00a0<\\/p><p style=\\\"line-height:1.38;margin-bottom:0pt;margin-top:0pt;\\\" dir=\\\"ltr\\\"><span style=\\\"background-color:transparent;color:#000000;font-family:Arial, sans-serif;font-size:13.999999999999998pt;\\\"><span style=\\\"font-style:normal;font-variant:normal;font-weight:400;text-decoration:none;vertical-align:baseline;white-space:pre-wrap;\\\">Our services are exc